			<section class="comment-content comment">
				<p>Why limit yourself to 2 or 3 shots when for the same money in the same size of package you could have 6 or 7? Don&#8217;t needlessly give yourself the &#8220;Biden handicap.&#8221;</p>
							</section><!-- .comment-content -->

			<div class="reply">
